Package: setpieces
Type: Package
Title: Extract and Analyze Football Set-Piece Events from Opta Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marc", "Lamberts", email = "waltzinganalytics@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to parse Opta MA1-style football event data and
    extract, classify, and analyze set pieces -- corners, free kicks,
    throw-ins, and penalties -- including delivery-zone breakdowns and
    second-ball contest detection.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    stats
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
